cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.RO 

This paper is about active learning in computer vision, specifically object detection. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of weak supervision and optimization, which suggests that it could also fit into the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the use of a switching condition for supervision level could relate to robotics and control, making cs.RO (Robotics) a possible category as well.
